high_descs: Turn right and walk around the chair to the side of the round black table.
Pick up the metal spoon that is closest to the potted plant on the round black table.
Walk over to where the microwave is on the counter and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the leftmost upper cabinet door and put the metal spoon in the bowl that is in the cabinet.
Pick up the bowl with the spoon in it and close the cabinet door.
Turn around and walk across the room to the chair, then turn right and walk up to the fridge, turn left and walk towards the wall then turn left again to face the round black table.
Put the bowl with the spoon in it on the round black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a spoon in it on a table.

high_descs: Go to the table table on the right.
Pick up the spoon on the table closest to the plant.
Go the the left to the wall.
Open the cupboard above the counter and place the spoon in the bowl.
Remove the bowl with the spoon from the cupboard and shut the door.
Turn around and go toward the wall and turn left toward the table.
Put the bowl and spoon on the table to right of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Get a bowl from a cupboard and bring it to the table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the chair then turn right and walk to the fridge then turn left and walk a step or two then turn left and walk to the table so you're to the right of the chair a little.
Pick up the spoon that's to the left of the pepper grinder.
Turn around and take a step then turn right and walk to the counter then take a step to your right and then walk all the way to the counter in front of you.
Look up and open the cupboard to your left and put the spoon in the bowl.
Pick up the bowl that's in the cupboard and close the door.
Go back to where you got the bowl.
Put the bowl with the spoon in it to the right of the remaining spoon on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a spoon in it on the table.
